N.Hristov, L. Georgieva) MANAGEMENT IN HEALTH CARE PRACTICE
A Handbook for Teachers, Researchers and Health Professionals
Title MANAGEMENT CYCLE: FROM PLANNING
TO EVALUATION Module: 2..1
