proportion: 30%/70%;
‚Ä¢ facilities: a class room;
‚Ä¢ equipment: computer, LCD projection equipment,
‚Ä¢ training materials: recommended readings or other related readings;
‚Ä¢ target audience: master degree students according to Bologna
scheme.
