Learning objectives Abstract MENTAL HEALTH IN COMMUNITY LIFE
ECTS (suggested): 0.5
Silvia-Gabriela Sc√Æntee, MD, MSc, PhD
Public Health Consultant
EHG Denmark
Adriana Galan
Public Health Consultant
Institute of Public Health Bucharest
Silvia-Gabriela Sc√Æntee
